Lamdas Used





  1. void populateCustomersTable() throws SQLException
    Where: CustomersTableController class
    Why: Lamdas were used to extract properties out of an array of Customer objects. They were beneficial here as new Customer objects did not have to be created, thus reducing the lines of code and lowering the time and space complexity.

    Why: Lamdas were used to extract properties out of an array of Appointment objects. They were beneficial here as new Appointment objects did not have to be created, thus reducing the lines of code and lowering the time and space complexity.
